STANDARD DEMAND FACTORY PACKAGE TO MANAGE SCENARIO EXECUTION.
!!! SCHEDULE THIS SCENARIO HOURLY WITH 4 REPETITIONS EVERY 15 MINUTES. THE SCENARIO WILL PROVIDE ITSELF TO RAISE AN ERRORE IF IT IS ALREADY RUNNING !!!
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- PACCHETTO STANDARD FACTORY DEMAND PER GESTIRE IL POLLING E L'ESECUZIONE DI SCENARI ODI.
!!! E' NECESSARIO SCHEDULARE LO SCENARIO DI QUESTO PACCHETTO OGNI ORA CON 4 RIPETIZIONI OGNI 15 MINUTI. SE LA SESSIONE E' GIA' RUNNING, IL PACCHETTO STESSO PROVVEDE A GENERARE ERRORE E USCIRE !!! -SCEN_STATUS=VALID
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("SNP_SESSION") ?> WHERE SESS_NAME = '<?=odiRef.getSession("SESS_NAME") ?>' AND SESS_STATUS='R'
SELECT SCEN_NAME, SCEN_VERSION, CONTEXT, AGENT_CODE FROM (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("ETL_SCENERY_EXECUTION") ?> WHERE FLG_EXEC=0 ORDER BY PRIORITY ASC) FIRST

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("ETL_SCENERY_EXECUTION") ?> SET START_DATE=GETDATE() , STATUS='Executing', FLG_EXEC=2, FLG_CHECK=0 WHERE SCEN_NAME='#SCEN_NAME' AND SCEN_VERSION='#SCEN_VERSION' AND CONTEXT='#CONTEXT' AND AGENT_CODE='#AGENT_CODE'
SELECT SCEN_NAME, SCEN_VERSION, CONTEXT, AGENT_CODE, SYNC_MODE FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("ETL_SCENERY_EXECUTION") ?> WHERE FLG_EXEC=2
UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("ETL_SCENERY_EXECUTION") ?> SET END_DATE=GETDATE(), STATUS='Waiting for update', FLG_EXEC=1 WHERE FLG_EXEC =2
UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("SNP_SESSION") ?> set SESS_BEG = dateadd(minute, -1, getdate()), SESS_END = dateadd(minute, -1, getdate()) where SESS_BEG is null
